DarkMouse::

She smiled. "I got the codes for everything in this base. What'cha 
need? I'm your mouse."  She looked up at Killfest. Herself standing 
at 5 foot tall, he towered over her.  But she still had something 
that even this giant of a bot didn't have. Her internal energon that 
flowed through her body.  She looked at the others in Killfest's 
group. Despite the size difference, she was going to like working for 
these guys.
